After a story that lasts around twelve hours – give or take a few, depending on how much of a hurry you’re in – it’s in these endlessly replayable bite-sized stages where the game’s longevity lies. How refreshing, too, to find that the maps have not simply been ripped from the campaign, instead carefully crafted to offer a range of tactical possibilities.
